01:09:50,415 --> 01:09:52,849
We're here, standing...

1263
01:09:52,918 --> 01:09:55,011
waiting... on you.

1264
01:09:55,087 --> 01:09:56,782
BUTLER:
I do beg your pardon, sir.

1265
01:09:56,855 --> 01:09:58,789
Tell him it's Flash Madden.

1266
01:09:58,857 --> 01:10:01,052
Now, go get him.
Show some huevos.

1267
01:10:01,126 --> 01:10:03,822
Pretentious prick,
act like he got a butler.

1268
01:10:03,895 --> 01:10:06,090
[Gate rattles...]

1269
01:10:08,000 --> 01:10:11,731
Anyway, this guy Moss
not only screws my wife...

1270
01:10:11,803 --> 01:10:13,771
