1276
01:10:42,134 --> 01:10:45,262
Oh, I see those standup
classes really paid off.

1277
01:10:45,337 --> 01:10:47,737
Up yours
and happy Hanukkah.

1278
01:10:47,806 --> 01:10:50,741
This here is Cameron.
He needs your help.

1279
01:10:50,809 --> 01:10:53,471
