1304
01:12:27,305 --> 01:12:29,296
Well, yours
is so fulfilled, right?

1305
01:12:29,374 --> 01:12:31,035
Don't confuse activity
with achievement.

1306
01:12:31,109 --> 01:12:34,044
I've seen those pieces of shit,
those celluloid abortions...

1307
01:12:34,112 --> 01:12:35,443
that you call movies.

1308
01:12:36,281 --> 01:12:38,078
Well, they weren't all stinkers.

1309
01:12:38,150 --> 01:12:40,482
Even won
a couple of brass dolls.

1310
01:12:41,386 --> 01:12:42,375
Three of them.

1311
01:12:43,655 --> 01:12:44,986
The picture business
has been good to me.

1312
01:12:45,056 --> 01:12:47,650
Oh, cut the bullshit.

1313
01:12:47,726 --> 01:12:50,718
That bullshit
is the reason you're here.

1314
01:12:54,633 --> 01:12:57,101
Yeah, all right, yeah.
You made your point.

1315
01:12:59,438 --> 01:13:00,427
So...

1316
01:13:01,573 --> 01:13:04,337
do we get the five large
or not?

1317
01:13:07,679 --> 01:13:10,170
Sure, Flash.

1318
01:13:11,616 --> 01:13:12,947
For old times' sake.

1319
01:13:19,791 --> 01:13:21,884
Listen, I'm sorry I screwed up
your life, Flash.

1320
01:13:21,960 --> 01:13:23,655
I didn't mean to
get you into all this.

1321
01:13:23,728 --> 01:13:25,787
A man has to kill
his own snakes.

1322
01:13:25,864 --> 01:13:28,424
You did me a solid today, Flash.

1323
01:13:28,500 --> 01:13:30,161
I owe you big time.

1324
01:13:31,470 --> 01:13:34,337
Yeah, well, we'll cash
the check tomorrow...

1325
01:13:34,406 --> 01:13:37,136
and uh, don't you worry, kid.

1326
01:13:37,209 --> 01:13:40,440
We'll get this epic of yours
on the road.

1327
01:13:51,990 --> 01:13:54,458
[Sleigh bells jingling...]

1328
01:13:57,863 --> 01:13:59,728
MILDRED: Two of hearts.

1329
01:13:59,798 --> 01:14:02,790
Ace of diamonds... a bullet!

1330
01:14:03,835 --> 01:14:07,601
And jack of clubs...

1331
01:14:07,672 --> 01:14:09,003
WOMAN ON TV:
So this is Holiday Inn.

1332
01:14:09,074 --> 01:14:10,905
[Flash turns off TV]

1333
01:14:27,759 --> 01:14:28,748
Well, I...

1334
01:14:29,761 --> 01:14:32,423
I could say
that I got buttered...

1335
01:14:32,497 --> 01:14:36,297
that Wild Turkey
did most of the talking...

1336
01:14:36,368 --> 01:14:39,303
but you know, I, I...

1337
01:14:39,371 --> 01:14:42,966
I've been hiding behind that
longer than I care to admit.

1338
01:14:46,778 --> 01:14:48,643
Surprise, surprise.

1339
01:14:58,523 --> 01:15:00,855
I'm real sorry
about what I-I s...

1340
01:15:02,460 --> 01:15:04,451
About last night.
I didn't mean what I said.

1341
01:15:04,529 --> 01:15:07,089
You're not forgotten souls.

1342
01:15:07,165 --> 01:15:09,497
You're not a bunch
of pathetic jerks.

1343
01:15:11,036 --> 01:15:13,300
Just me.

1344
01:15:23,682 --> 01:15:25,377
MAN: So?

1345
01:15:26,885 --> 01:15:31,015
Does that kid still want us
to make his movie or not?

1346
01:15:31,089 --> 01:15:35,048
Well, we raised
a little money today...

1347
01:15:35,126 --> 01:15:40,029
and it looks like we're back on
if-if... if you still wanna...

1348
01:15:41,900 --> 01:15:42,889
Yes, Montana?

1349
01:15:43,835 --> 01:15:45,166
What time is call?

1350
01:15:46,504 --> 01:15:48,404
Seven A.M., Monday morning.

1351
01:15:48,473 --> 01:15:50,498
- Then we're in.
- Vin!

1352
01:15:50,575 --> 01:15:53,271
- Why the hell not?!
- [All exclaim and applaud]

1353
01:15:55,280 --> 01:15:58,681
I think you lot are insane.
All of you!

1354
01:15:58,750 --> 01:16:03,414
Oh, goddamn it, you...
you folks are the best.

1355
01:16:03,488 --> 01:16:04,921
MILDRED: Goody goody!

1356
01:16:04,990 --> 01:16:09,290
[Tearfully] That kid is so lucky
to have you on his team.

1357
01:16:09,361 --> 01:16:11,522
Ah, it's your team too, Flash.

1358
01:16:11,596 --> 01:16:13,257
I guess I'm lucky, too.

1359
01:16:13,331 --> 01:16:15,231
We're gonna make a movie!

1360
01:16:15,300 --> 01:16:16,426
All right!

1361
01:16:16,501 --> 01:16:17,490
[Applause]

1362
01:16:19,638 --> 01:16:21,401
[Flash sobs]

1363
01:16:21,473 --> 01:16:24,408
It's O.K. We love you, Flash.

1364
01:16:27,112 --> 01:16:29,137
