Definitely not good.

1598
01:29:30,494 --> 01:29:31,859
[Whooshing]

1599
01:29:31,929 --> 01:29:33,760
Hey, roll on this.

1600
01:29:33,831 --> 01:29:35,196
All right, you got it.

1601
01:29:37,435 --> 01:29:40,404
- This looks familiar, right?
- I'm feelin' you, dude.

1602
01:29:40,471 --> 01:29:42,939
Dogs and humans,
there's no difference.

1603
01:29:43,007 --> 01:29:43,996
[Gate rattles]

1604
01:29:45,443 --> 01:29:47,343
Flash, what the hell...

1605
01:29:47,411 --> 01:29:48,605
[Dogs barking...]

1606
01:29:48,679 --> 01:29:50,010
CAMERON:
What the hell you doing?

1607
01:29:50,080 --> 01:29:51,069
I'm settin' 'em free.

1608
01:29:51,148 --> 01:29:52,740
What the hell
do you think I'm doing?

1609
01:29:52,817 --> 01:29:54,375
MURPHY: Shit, Cameron.
We can't get busted again.

1610
01:29:54,452 --> 01:29:55,783
CAMERON:
Murph's right, Flash. We can't...

1611
01:29:55,853 --> 01:29:58,651
Murph's a coward just like
that son of a bitch, Nietzsche!

1612
01:29:58,722 --> 01:30:01,316
Hey! Go on then!

1613
01:30:02,092 --> 01:30:03,081
[Puppies barking]

1614
01:30:03,627 --> 01:30:05,254
FLASH: Oh! Hey!

1615
01:30:05,329 --> 01:30:07,092
Let my people go!

1616
01:30:07,164 --> 01:30:08,688
Run, doggies!

1617
01:30:08,766 --> 01:30:11,030
CAMERON:
Run where, Flash, where?

1618
01:30:11,101 --> 01:30:13,228
- Hey, I know a place.
- Where?

1619
01:30:13,304 --> 01:30:15,238
- Get the truck!
- CAMERON: Flash, we can't!

1620
01:30:15,306 --> 01:30:17,240
- MURPHY: No, no way.
- You're pussies!

1621
01:30:17,308 --> 01:30:19,674
- I'll get it myself.
- Flash, this is not cool!

1622
01:30:19,743 --> 01:30:21,574
This is grand theft auto, O. K?

1623
01:30:21,645 --> 01:30:22,942
And I know a little
something about it...

1624
01:30:23,013 --> 01:30:24,002
and I won't do it again!

1625
01:30:24,081 --> 01:30:27,949
I am not leavin'
without those dogs!

1626
01:30:28,018 --> 01:30:30,248
I mean, they're gonna kill 'em!

1627
01:30:30,321 --> 01:30:31,310
Don't you care?

1628
01:30:32,056 --> 01:30:33,717
Flash, of course I care.

1629
01:30:34,959 --> 01:30:36,950
After all I've done for you...

1630
01:30:37,027 --> 01:30:39,495
you can't do this one
small thing for me?

1631
01:30:39,563 --> 01:30:42,225
This one small felony.

1632
01:30:44,802 --> 01:30:47,566
FLASH: Yeah, I know
a dog park in Boyle Heights.

1633
01:30:47,638 --> 01:30:48,969
Yeah, at least dumping dogs
in a dog park...

1634
01:30:49,039 --> 01:30:50,028
is only a misdemeanor.

1635
01:30:50,107 --> 01:30:52,007
Who goes to dog parks?

1636
01:30:52,076 --> 01:30:54,476
Dog owners, dog lovers,
people who give a shit.

1637
01:30:54,545 --> 01:30:55,944
CAMERON: Yeah,
but they already have dogs.

1638
01:30:56,013 --> 01:30:57,412
That's why they go there.

1639
01:30:57,481 --> 01:30:58,470
And it's midnight.

1640
01:30:58,549 --> 01:31:00,141
No one's even gonna be
there right now anyway.

1641
01:31:00,217 --> 01:31:01,445
FLASH: Yeah, I know that,
but in the morning...

1642
01:31:01,519 --> 01:31:03,510
when the dog lovers
show up, hey, who knows?

1643
01:31:03,587 --> 01:31:04,986
The dogs may get lucky and...

1644
01:31:05,055 --> 01:31:06,522
Dog people are crazy.

1645
01:31:06,590 --> 01:31:09,150
They're nuts!
When they get together...

1646
01:31:09,226 --> 01:31:11,660
it's worse than an A.A. meeting.

1647
01:31:11,729 --> 01:31:14,061
But the bottom line is
they love dogs...

1648
01:31:14,131 --> 01:31:16,691
more than life itself,
and that's perfect for us.

1649
01:31:16,767 --> 01:31:19,292
And our seventeen friends.

1650
01:31:25,876 --> 01:31:27,207
See, Flash?

1651
01:31:27,278 --> 01:31:28,939
Eh, they don't mean it.

1652
01:31:29,914 --> 01:31:31,211
Open it up.

1653
01:31:33,851 --> 01:31:36,979
[Dogs whimpering and barking]

1654
01:31:42,660 --> 01:31:44,924
Ain't that a pretty sight.

1655
01:31:49,867 --> 01:31:52,665
I have to admit,
they are a happy bunch.

1656
01:31:52,736 --> 01:31:55,534
Right, but animal control'll
come and pick 'em up tomorrow.

1657
01:31:56,640 --> 01:31:58,301
At least they have tonight.

1658
01:31:59,543 --> 01:32:00,601
