left to be mean to.

1708
01:34:19,083 --> 01:34:22,143
And on that day...
hey, hey, hey, you die.

1709
01:34:22,820 --> 01:34:24,811
What crap.

1710
01:34:27,024 --> 01:34:30,118
I've been meaner than
a snake to most people I know.

1711
01:34:30,194 --> 01:34:31,957
But now that I'm
at the end of my game...

1712
01:34:32,029 --> 01:34:33,758
there are precious few left.

1713
01:34:33,831 --> 01:34:35,492
My ass bleeds for you.

1714
01:34:37,301 --> 01:34:39,565
Yeah, felt good for you
to say that, didn't it?

1715
01:34:39,636 --> 01:34:41,035
As a matter of fact, it did.

1716
01:34:41,105 --> 01:34:42,231
Yeah, I know.

1717
01:34:42,306 --> 01:34:44,638
I used to take great pleasure
in doing shit like that.

1718
01:34:44,708 --> 01:34:46,699
- I was a master at it.
- Fascinating.

1719
01:34:46,777 --> 01:34:50,213
Listen to me,
you dim-witted mud hook.

1720
01:34:50,280 --> 01:34:52,248
I'm trying to tell you
something...

1721
01:34:52,316 --> 01:34:54,250
