your ears boxed...

1724
01:34:58,822 --> 01:35:00,289
I'll gladly oblige.

1725
01:35:00,357 --> 01:35:01,881
I know I may be getting on
in years...

1726
01:35:01,959 --> 01:35:04,086
but I could still
knock you off the porch.

1727
01:35:04,161 --> 01:35:06,425
You get my meaning,
simpleton?

1728
01:35:08,265 --> 01:35:11,564
Now lay off Cameron.
He's good people.

1729
01:35:11,635 --> 01:35:15,230
He doesn't like me...
and I don't like him.

1730
01:35:15,305 --> 01:35:18,240
Well, I don't like you either,
but I love that boy.

1731
01:35:18,308 --> 01:35:19,969
I'm happy for you. [Chuckles]

1732
01:35:21,044 --> 01:35:23,103
You don't get it, do you?

1733
01:35:24,715 --> 01:35:28,378
You don't see his worth, do you?

1734
01:35:30,654 --> 01:35:33,521
But mark my words...

1735
01:35:33,590 --> 01:35:36,184
that boy'll make you proud...

1736
01:35:38,729 --> 01:35:40,526
if you just give him a chance.

1737
01:35:44,468 --> 01:35:46,026
Huh?

1738
01:35:47,437 --> 01:35:48,426
Ah, come on.

1739
01:35:50,073 --> 01:35:53,042
[Choir singing faintly]

1740
01:35:54,545 --> 01:35:56,479
FLASH: Hey, Cameron...

1741
01:35:56,547 --> 01:35:59,516
we were just listing
your shortcomings.

1742
01:36:01,018 --> 01:36:02,315
I know, I gotta do better.

1743
01:36:02,386 --> 01:36:04,752
FLASH: Oh... my God.

1744
01:36:04,822 --> 01:36:06,551
Mother Kincaid...

1745
01:36:06,623 --> 01:36:09,820
what a culinary wizard
you turned out to be.

1746
01:36:09,893 --> 01:36:13,090
- Well, she's the best, right?
- She is.

1747
01:36:15,465 --> 01:36:16,932
Thank you, honey.

1748
01:36:17,000 --> 01:36:18,797
Here, Floyd. Here you go.

1749
01:36:18,869 --> 01:36:21,838
Thank you.

1750
01:36:21,905 --> 01:36:24,305
So how's your movie coming?

1751
01:36:24,374 --> 01:36:25,898
Huh?

1752
01:36:25,976 --> 01:36:27,409
Oh...

1753
01:36:27,477 --> 01:36:30,810
It's good. We're editing now.

1754
01:36:30,881 --> 01:36:32,542
I'd like to see it.

1755
01:36:33,984 --> 01:36:35,781
Yeah, as soon as it's done.

1756
01:36:35,853 --> 01:36:37,480
JUD Y: I can't wait.

1757
01:36:37,554 --> 01:36:40,523
- Flash is the man.
- Ah.

1758
01:36:40,591 --> 01:36:42,525
I could not have done it
without this man here.

1759
01:36:42,593 --> 01:36:45,585
And the entire west wing of
the Motion Picture Residence.

1760
01:36:45,662 --> 01:36:47,960
[Applauding]

1761
01:36:49,466 --> 01:36:52,094
Hey, the toast then, huh?

1762
01:36:55,272 --> 01:36:57,263
Let me think, let me think.

1763
01:36:58,108 --> 01:37:01,976
Even though we may fall
into misfortune...

